  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK897">
<l>vakaimāṇṭa vāḻkkaiyum vāṉporuḷu meṉṉān</l>
<l>takaimāṇṭa takkār ceṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a king incurs the wrath of the righteous great, what will become of his government with its splendid auxiliaries and (all) its untold wealth ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
